            "Answer: $7.8 \\times 10^{-5}$"
          ]
        },
        {
          "part": "c",
          "instruction": "Calculate",
          "expression": "$(3 \\times 10^4) \\times (2 \\times 10^5)$",
          "answer": "$6 \\times 10^9$",
          "solution_steps": [
            "Multiply coefficients: $3 \\times 2 = 6$",
            "Add exponents: $10^4 \\times 10^5 = 10^{4+5} = 10^9$",
